    public class PurchaseOrder
extends PurchaseByVendor
implements Serializable, org.jvnet.jaxb2_commons.lang.Equals2, org.jvnet.jaxb2_commons.lang.HashCode2
    PurchaseOrder is a non-posting transaction representing a request to purchase goods or services from a third party.

    Java class for PurchaseOrder complex type.
